-- Barclays Says Head of Loan Capital Markets for Asia to Retire
-- B y   W e n d y   M o c k
-- 2012-05-04T08:40:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-04/barclays-says-head-of-loan-capital-markets-for-asia-to-retire.html
Richard Palmer will retire as head of
loan capital markets for the Asia-Pacific region at  Barclays
Plc (BARC) , according to Angie Tang, a Hong Kong-based spokewoman at
the London-listed bank.  Guy Smith and Richard Satchwell have been named as co-heads
of loan capital markets to replace Palmer, Tang said in a phone
interview today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wendy Mock in Hong Kong at 
 wmock3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shelley Smith at 
 ssmith118@bloomberg.net  